1 (g)(1) This section shall not apply to a firearms transfer at a gun show.
2 (2) As used in this subsection, “gun show” means a function sponsored
3 by:
4 (A) a national, state, or local organization, devoted to the collection,
5 competitive use, or other sporting use of firearms; or
6 (B) an organization or association that sponsors functions devoted to
7 the collection, competitive use, or other sporting use of firearms in the
8 community.
